<p>ç°åº¦æˆªæ­¢å€¼ grey level cutoff value</p>

<ul>
  <li>1 (binary images, â€œbitmapsâ€) â†’ 1 bit/pixel</li>
  <li>255 â†’ 8 bit/pixel = 1 byte/pixel</li>
  <li>4095 â†’ 12 bit/pixel = 1.5 byte/pixel</li>
  <li>65535 â†’ 16 bit/pixel = 2 byte/pixel</li>
</ul>

