<p>è¿‡åº¦æ›å…‰çš„å›¾åƒï¼š â€¢ ç”±äºæˆªæ­¢å€¼å¯¼è‡´ä¿¡æ¯ä¸¢å¤±ï¼Œæ— æ³•é‡å»º â€¢ ç›¸æœºå…‰åœˆå…³é—­ â€¢ å‡å°‘ç›¸æœºæ›å…‰æ—¶é—´ â€¢ è‡ªåŠ¨æ›å…‰ Overexposed images: â€¢ information loss due to cutoff value, no reconstruction possible â€¢ close aperture of camera â€¢ reduce exposure time of camera â€¢ auto-exposure</p>

<p><img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/WenboLi-CN-DE/Picture/main/20220316210355.png" alt="" /></p>

\[\gamma = 1\]

